          "step": "Find common denominator $(x + 2)(x - 1)$",
          "calculation": "$\\frac{x(x - 1)}{(x + 2)(x - 1)} - \\frac{3(x + 2)}{(x + 2)(x - 1)}$"
        },
        {
          "step": "Combine numerators",
          "calculation": "$\\frac{x^2 - x - 3x - 6}{(x + 2)(x - 1)} = \\frac{x^2 - 4x - 6}{(x + 2)(x - 1)}$"
        }
      ],
      "final_answer": "$\\frac{x^2 - 4x - 6}{(x + 2)(x - 1)}$"
